  All code involving engine management or UI interaction is DroidFish-derived.
  - MainActivity.java: AGPL v3 → GPL v3 (UI interaction — WebView host)
  - ChessWebViewClient.java: AGPL v3 → GPL v3 (UI interaction — WebView client)
  - EngineService.java: AGPL v3 → GPL v3 (engine management — foreground service)
  - StatsActivity.java: AGPL v3 → GPL v3 (UI interaction + PGN display)
  - StabilizationHelper.java: AGPL v3 → GPL v3 (UI interaction — board stabilization)
  Files REMAINING AGPL v3: ChessApp.java (infrastructure), RootDetector.java (security),
  TlsSecurityHelper.java (TLS config) — not chess/engine/PGN/UI code.
  No functional code changes — license-header-only.

