v1.1.2 Phase 71 (2026.7.11, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3): three fixes.
    (1) readyOkLatchHolder race — JS binder thread (sendSetOptionAndWait) and
        executor thread (startEngineInternal / engineGoInternal ucinewgame)
        both wrote the single volatile field without synchronization; if they
        overlapped, one latch was lost → 3s/10s timeout. Fix: dedicated
        _readyOkLock serializes all readyOk set+wait operations.
    (2) engineStop TOCTOU on _discardingPonderBestmove — engineStop set the
        flag outside any lock while the reader thread's bestmove handler read
        it outside any lock. Fix: dedicated _discardFlagLock makes the
        check-and-clear atomic w.r.t. engineStop's set.
    (3) importSettings cap bypass — direct field assignment with loose caps
        (1024/1048576/10000) bypassed Phase 69 setter caps (2x CPU cores / 50%
        JVM heap / 1000ms). Fix: apply Phase 69 cap formulas inline in
        importSettings (direct assignment necessary because setters return
        early when autoConfig is enabled — autoConfig is disabled later in
        the import flow).
  - StatsActivity.java (GPL v3): added deprecated shouldOverrideUrlLoading
    overload (API 21-23 compat — only the deprecated overload fires on those
    API levels; without it, external http(s) URLs would load INTO the WebView
    bypassing the system browser). Added onRenderProcessGone handler so a
    render-process crash on the stats page finishes the activity instead of
    leaving a blank WebView. Shared URL-override logic extracted to
    _handleUrlOverride(String) helper.
  - Other Java files: No changes.
  - License classification unchanged.

