v1.1.2 Phase 69 (2026.7.9, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - StockfishNative.java (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived): UCI parameter validation
    tightened per SF18 best-practices PDF guide:
    * MultiPV cap 8 (was 500; PDF recommends 3-5 for review).
    * Move Overhead cap 1000ms (was 5000ms; PDF recommends 10-30 local, 50-150 network).
    * Hash cap 50% of JVM heap (was 32TB; PDF warns swapping kills performance).
    * Threads cap 2x CPU cores (was 512; PDF warns thread contention reduces NPS).
    * Added UCI_AnalyseMode=true during eval mode (applyEvalModeOptions) +
      UCI_AnalyseMode=false restore for gameplay (restoreGameplayOptions).
  - Other Java files: no changes.
  - License classification unchanged.

